Subject: Avoid installation of python-setuptools-git.

Remove setuptools_git from pip-requires so that it is not automatically
added to the dependency list by dh_python2, and avoid having it and its
dependencies (git!) installed with python-nova.

diff -Naurp nova-2013.1.orig/setup.py nova-2013.1/setup.py
--- nova-2013.1.orig/setup.py	2013-01-01 23:04:36.000000000 -0600
+++ nova-2013.1/setup.py	2013-01-02 07:50:05.081000609 -0600
@@ -43,7 +43,6 @@ setuptools.setup(name='nova',
       install_requires=requires,
       include_package_data=True,
       test_suite='nose.collector',
-      setup_requires=['setuptools_git>=0.4'],
       scripts=['bin/nova-all',
                'bin/nova-api',
                'bin/nova-api-ec2',
diff -Naurp nova-2013.1.orig/tools/pip-requires nova-2013.1/tools/pip-requires
--- nova-2013.1.orig/tools/pip-requires	2013-01-01 23:04:36.000000000 -0600
+++ nova-2013.1/tools/pip-requires	2013-01-02 07:49:48.285000601 -0600
@@ -19,7 +19,6 @@ paramiko
